OL,6, meetings harmed the UK's response to   
OL,7, the pandemic, Sadiq Khan and Andy      
OL,8, Burnham have told the Covid inquiry.   
OL,10,FThe Labour mayors of London and Greater
OL,11,FManchester said their repeated requests
OL,12,Fto join emergency Cobra meetings at the
OL,13,Fstart of the pandemic were refused.    
